Check out 
@pandadoc
 - the complete solution for client-facing #salesdocuments Love it! http://pandadoc.cc/2nwYyZT

Just cancelled a $50 monthly subscription to Pandadoc that we have been using to send our agency proposals for years now! We vibe coded our own system complete with agreement signing and payment integration using 
@orchidsapp
 - we have a few more such subscriptions that we will be canceling and replace with vibe coded systems in the coming weeks!!

Interesting that if you cancel a document with
@docusign
, it still comes off your quota. Plus,
@pandadoc
s free plan is currently better than my DocuSign paid plan. Don't think I'll be renewing.

I thought the days were gone when cancelling or downgrading a subscription would require email or chat with support. 
@pandadoc
 doesn't allow you to downgrade your subscription and even chat takes 18hrs to respond to carry out one action
